{"word":"Synagogue","slug":"synagogue","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Synagogue</b> 1. Primarily an assembly:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=43'>Act 13:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=2&verse=2'>Jas 2:2</a> <br/> - Constitutes a court of justice<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=12&verse=11'>Luk 12:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=2'>Act 9:2</a> <br/> - Had powers of criminal courts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=17'>Mat 10:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=23&verse=34'>Mat 23:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=19'>Act 22:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=26&verse=11'>Act 26:11</a> <br/> - Of ecclesiastical courts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=9&verse=22'>Joh 9:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=9&verse=34'>Joh 9:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=42'>Joh 12:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=16&verse=2'>Joh 16:2</a> <br/> 2. Place of assembly:<br/> - Scriptures read and expounded in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=8'>Neh 8:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=3'>Neh 9:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=5'>Neh 9:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=23'>Mat 4:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=35'>Mat 9:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=54'>Mat 13:54</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=39'>Mar 1:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.